in which you work and the results
you hope to obtain. 

43
00:02:42,319 --> 00:02:46,132
Well, the approach as in, you need 
to draw up the sampling plan

44
00:02:46,327 --> 00:02:49,727
that will ensure obtained results
will be as usable, precise,

45
00:02:49,985 --> 00:02:51,510
and correct as possible. 

46
00:02:51,765 --> 00:02:54,877
You can then proceed to counting
all the individuals

47
00:02:55,075 --> 00:02:57,825
 near water point
if the species is localized 

48
