What maters in this step
is to follow drawer pools 

55
00:03:22,828 --> 00:03:25,503
and to do the work
with precision. 

56
00:03:25,736 --> 00:03:29,049
If you don't, you give way 
to an acceptable bias

57
00:03:29,260 --> 00:03:31,210
for the data processing.

58
00:03:32,154 --> 00:03:34,254
And the data collected
should be stored 

59
00:03:34,481 --> 00:03:38,231
and remain available for future use
because they guarantee 

60
00:03:38,472 --> 00:03:41,722
the truthfulness and the reliability
of the monitoring. 

61
